{"id": "ChIJ-2eKFNCkwoARWyDU48bVkwM", "rating": 4.1, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 464, "displayName": {"text": "Go Greek Yogurt", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJ-2eKFNCkwoARWyDU48bVkwM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Zd2MyZFpiV2g1TWtGWVNVc3lWVEU1WmxWdFVsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 1, "text": {"text": "I’ve been a fan for a long time, however, on my recent visit to Santa Monica location I was horrified by the lack of cleanliness and order.   The store was not busy, cashier was on TikTok with her hair in the topping bar.   The topping bar was also in disarray.   For a brand who positions itself as a premium product, with premium prices - this experience does not match", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "I’ve been a fan for a long time, however, on my recent visit to Santa Monica location I was horrified by the lack of cleanliness and order.   The store was not busy, cashier was on TikTok with her hair in the topping bar.   The topping bar was also in disarray.   For a brand who positions itself as a premium product, with premium prices - this experience does not match", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Tavia Blount", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/108610168742713741043/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVTQIwiCq7CTNrrEwLnQP7lr0u9SUmWQOd90aZhNcSNJkW1hQz7=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-23T03:14:32.817674033Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Zd2MyZFpiV2g1TWtGWVNVc3lWVEU1WmxWdFVsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT21Zd2MyZFpiV2g1TWtGWVNVc3lWVEU1WmxWdFVsRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4d0148a67fb:0x393d5c6e3d4205b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-2eKFNCkwoARWyDU48bVkwM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3NFFUZEtOWHBEVldSelpFTmpTV1JzZVVZdFVXYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "Go Greek was good! I really enjoyed the tart frozen yogurt and the cherry natural yogurt was delicious too. The space is clean with a nice, modern ambiance, and there are outdoor tables if you want to sit outside. Service was attentive and friendly. Prices are on the higher side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Go Greek was good! I really enjoyed the tart frozen yogurt and the cherry natural yogurt was delicious too. The space is clean with a nice, modern ambiance, and there are outdoor tables if you want to sit outside. Service was attentive and friendly. Prices are on the higher side.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mayi Barov", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/105050300904308996068/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUDc99F-mEYJXEP7OFoHDROcQNIiEFF2aIK3NShcwSe-_EyHRlaFA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2025-06-27T05:57:42.748261525Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3NFFUZEtOWHBEVldSelpFTmpTV1JzZVVZdFVXYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2t3NFFUZEtOWHBEVldSelpFTmpTV1JzZVVZdFVXYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4d0148a67fb:0x393d5c6e3d4205b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-2eKFNCkwoARWyDU48bVkwM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214QlZXWldWVVJpUW5SZmJGQnlhVVJKVVU1MFptYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "4 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Great location - right by the beach. Good number of toppings: fruit, chocolate, chia seeds, granola, candies, etc. and a selection of yogurts (we mixed strawberry and plain). The store is self-service so you can choose how much you want of everything. Careful with the pricing as a bowl fills up fast, but definitely recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Great location - right by the beach. Good number of toppings: fruit, chocolate, chia seeds, granola, candies, etc. and a selection of yogurts (we mixed strawberry and plain). The store is self-service so you can choose how much you want of everything. Careful with the pricing as a bowl fills up fast, but definitely recommend.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Jessie Brockmann", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/114872608260820799208/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW3AzSS7ePWUO0ZeROhJ2-mnv4lQ8wx9nRs0woTC9-HMpm_hFQc1g=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-13T07:09:20.154277669Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214QlZXWldWVVJpUW5SZmJGQnlhVVJKVVU1MFptYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT214QlZXWldWVVJpUW5SZmJGQnlhVVJKVVU1MFptYxAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4d0148a67fb:0x393d5c6e3d4205b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-2eKFNCkwoARWyDU48bVkwM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pFeE4xUktWWFZ4YTFSek1Ea3RPSFJyYTFKQk5FRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "6 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "One of my favorite spots in town for froyo especially when I am craving for simple plain tart one instead of anything flavored. The Santa Monica one is preferred for me given plenty of available parking structure and its most accessible location, despite the fact that it has shorter opening time compared to Beverly Hills one.\n\nYou may have known the drill that it's self-service, weight-based option, so you pay as you take.\n\nI'd say Go Greek is tad more pricey than 'it's comparable peers', but the bold and fresh tangy flavor does make it worth. Besides, you can enjoy your froyo while enjoying Santa Monica beach view.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "One of my favorite spots in town for froyo especially when I am craving for simple plain tart one instead of anything flavored. The Santa Monica one is preferred for me given plenty of available parking structure and its most accessible location, despite the fact that it has shorter opening time compared to Beverly Hills one.\n\nYou may have known the drill that it's self-service, weight-based option, so you pay as you take.\n\nI'd say Go Greek is tad more pricey than 'it's comparable peers', but the bold and fresh tangy flavor does make it worth. Besides, you can enjoy your froyo while enjoying Santa Monica beach view.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "JG", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/111257583310582062343/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjX8UqbsVHg2VxS0LgD7ECyFYYeCZ3BA4Dt0ktxf3VxgqHOQs4o=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba6"}, "publishTime": "2026-01-06T22:34:16.172225535Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pFeE4xUktWWFZ4YTFSek1Ea3RPSFJyYTFKQk5FRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pFeE4xUktWWFZ4YTFSek1Ea3RPSFJyYTFKQk5FRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4d0148a67fb:0x393d5c6e3d4205b"}, {"name": "places/ChIJ-2eKFNCkwoARWyDU48bVkwM/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wNFozcEJZVVEwTFY5WmJsRklXbVpmTFc5V09WRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a month ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "The frozen yogurt itself was genuinely delicious — great quality, fresh fruit, and really good texture. Staff was also polite and took the time to double-check my receipt when I asked about the price. But $17 after tax for a relatively small frozen yogurt is hard to justify. That’s almost the price of a full Sweetgreen salad, which is already considered expensive, except that’s an actual meal.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "The frozen yogurt itself was genuinely delicious — great quality, fresh fruit, and really good texture. Staff was also polite and took the time to double-check my receipt when I asked about the price. But $17 after tax for a relatively small frozen yogurt is hard to justify. That’s almost the price of a full Sweetgreen salad, which is already considered expensive, except that’s an actual meal.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Françoise Ouapeu", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/102618346358873716509/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVf5RgptxxKMFBvISpFpq5FWvqvFxTb2Wgodzpzmnse4Zb6z6PrKA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-05-17T01:53:36.644442147Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wNFozcEJZVVEwTFY5WmJsRklXbVpmTFc5V09WRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT20wNFozcEJZVVEwTFY5WmJsRklXbVpmTFc5V09WRRAB!2m1!1s0x80c2a4d0148a67fb:0x393d5c6e3d4205b"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJ-2eKFNCkwoARWyDU48bVkwM/photos/AWCwydh4QBsjLYcX2YMxy9YpBP6MRYwuDpz0jCgBSqTtHHP4qM6XcU6_di2BIvALB_FvrRXlLXWPWIt_cjdn2FSq-st05guOZqSDEtrO2_a-2ohR6GeFW1pGRqM3FGcUEne5mUjX4cNUo0h7Fv-RKxGt-st95h-OOIYa8eX5E3R6BYMcA3-Nxj-U7z03cCtN6Wjoy_EO7j3D5yzJf00V4Fnx40g5j4u77zAsO8gvmDTjSaE2jv_9vRuPPYKeW3O-ghHYnLWa29pJcfTgnAD25KeWd4LnYUXlDjNQ0DJGvrPPvmbeA0WiCeVUXQyWj0gLNEYQBTTmso_qx3CnnO47tT1nEG4Ch8YEAMREZqiYOe1tCgKTLMINVw7TkuVe9fGfSTa5IklryajI9ZeHY9EMAI8NLmixRDOk04toNx0yrVRnIlpZE2oCc4ov7iGqXANJ0L1_", "widthPx": 4032, "heightPx": 3024, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "Michael M", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/115319872164886687916", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjWt6JuVnMCKMUBRFqAfqkw4j-LqGy39xUQiOinjWy5tQCDlgck=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIABIhDyDFQ7YqCNkNWSFK22mcRz&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1